程序包 org.giiwa.bean

类 GLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.giiwa.dao.Bean
      • org.giiwa.bean.GLog

  • public class GLog
extends Bean
    Operation Log bean.
    Used to record info/warn/error log in database
    Beside this, the module also can add personal ILogger for other use by OpLog.addLogger()
    table="gi_oplog"

    yjiang
